<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>td â€” simple task tracker</title>
    <meta name="description" content="SQLite task tracker for AI agents. Single bash script." />
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      
      :root {
        --bg: #fff;
        --fg: #111;
        --muted: #666;
        --border: #e5e5e5;
        --code-bg: #f5f5f5;
        --font: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        --mono: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
      }
      
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        :root {
          --bg: #111;
          --fg: #eee;
          --muted: #888;
          --border: #333;
          --code-bg: #1a1a1a;
        }
      }
      
      html {
        font-family: var(--font);
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--fg);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      
      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      
      main {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 480px;
        padding: 3rem;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      
      p {
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      
      p:last-of-type {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      code {
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        background: var(--code-bg);
        padding: 0.15rem 0.35rem;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }
      
      .install {
        display: block;
        background: var(--code-bg);
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
      
      footer {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
      }
      
      a { color: var(--fg); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>td</h1>
      
      <p>A task tracker for AI coding agents. I liked <a href="https://github.com/steveyegge/beads">beads</a>, but it became more than I wanted. So I made this.</p>
      
      <p>One bash script. SQLite. No setup.</p>
      
      <code class="install">curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alosec/td-world/main/install.sh | bash</code>
      
      <p>Also includes <code>tv</code>, an fzf viewer.</p>
      
      <footer><a href="https://github.com/alosec/td-world">GitHub</a></footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
